title: Person1_Talk
---
<<if $quest_completed>>
    Person_1: Thanks again for helping me out earlier.
<<elseif $quest_active>>
    Person_1: Have you delivered my message to Person 2 yet?
    Person_1: They should be nearby.
<<else>>
    <<jump Person1_FirstMeeting>>
<<endif>>
