title: Person1_FirstMeeting
---
Person_1: Oh, hello there!
Person_1: I wonder if you could help me with something?

-> Sure, what do you need?
    <<jump Person1_GiveQuest>>

-> Sorry, I'm in a hurry.
    Person_1: No worries, perhaps another time.
===

title: Person1_GiveQuest
---
Person_1: Excellent! I need you to deliver a message to Person 2.
Person_1: Tell them that the meeting has been moved to Thursday.
Person_1: Can you do that for me?

-> Consider it done.
    <<set $quest_active to true>>
    Person_1: Thank you so much! They should be somewhere nearby.
    <<stop>>

-> Actually, I'm busy right now.
    Person_1: Oh, that's a shame. Come back if you change your mind.
    <<stop>>
===